casebody.data:
FLORIDA, plaintiff,
v.
GEORGIA. No. 142 Original. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 17, 2016.

The motion of the Special Master for allowance of fees and disbursements is granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $57,333, for the period February 1, 2016, through August 31, 2016, to be paid equally by the parties.
